Preconditions:
- The input array `nums` is not null.
- The length of the input array `nums` is greater than or equal to 2.

Postconditions:
- The elements in the input array `nums` are reordered such that `nums[0] < nums[1] > nums[2] < nums[3]...`.
- The relative order of the elements that satisfy the above condition is maintained.
- The elements that do not satisfy the above condition may have any order among themselves.
- The input array `nums` is modified in-place.